## Users
The `users` table in the app database is used to sync IDs with the Better Auth database so constraints can be enforced in the app database. A record is added to the app database `users` table in the registration hook.

## Issues 
**database** src/db/schema/issues.ts
**module** src/modules/issues

### Create
**path** (restricted)/[slug]/projects/[id]/issues/new

### Edit
**path** (restricted)/[slug]/projects/[id]/issues/edit/[issueId]

### View
**path** (restricted)/[slug]/projects/[id]/issues/[issueId]

### List
**path** (restricted)/[slug]/projects/[id]/issues
**UI** tanstack table to display issues. Click on row displays issue view.